# S2-6: Public API Documentation

This task involves documenting the Collective Unconscious API using Swagger/OpenAPI. This will provide an interactive UI for developers to explore endpoints, understand request/response structures, and test the API directly.

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> I will be using `swagger-jsdoc` to generate the OpenAPI specification from JSDoc comments in the code and `swagger-ui-express` to serve the interactive documentation at `/api-docs`.

